<br>
Frankly the only bannings that should take place on the rant forum are the porn/advertisement/spam variety.  If people want to come here and be fucktards, this is their place to do it.  As long as we have a definition, amongst moderators, as to what spam is - voila, no problems.<br>
<br>
As for getting the mods to agree on banning a problem child - it can be weeks before mods all get a chance to visit the forums and respond.  You really want to wait that long for intervention?  I don't.  <br>
<br>
You can weigh this forum down with rules, or you can be adults and moderate it the way it should be moderated - gently, fairly, invisibly, and without turning the attention to yourself or using your four-letter prowess to do it.  <br>
<br>
That, of course, is just my opinion.  <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:green;font-family:georgia;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Meridian Ascendant</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
