<br>
For example: If a poster wants to come here and rant about how shitty American Chinese food is compared to authentic Hu Nan style duck you get in mainland China, I could give a fuck what his in-game name is.<br>
<br>
If said poster wants to come here and talk about how seven members of Gray Council robbed his trade mule, took all his items and plat, trained him until he lost seventeen levels, then drove over to his house and buttfucked his poodle until it died... then fuck yes. I want to know who's making the god damned allegations. And if they won't back it up with their Xev ID, then ban their fucking asses.<br>
<br>
The rule allows that.  I would hope to fuck that whatever mods we have can be trusted for the miniscule level of maturity and common fucking sense it would take to discern between the two. <p>Jakiss Enkokiss<br>
