<br>
Call me crazy, but here's my idea:<br>
There are two types of idiots that can be banned....those that are obvious (porn, pyramid schemes, etc) and those that aren't quite so obvious, or would be contested, like with the name rule.<br>
First moderator to run across type 1 bans them, as is usual.<br>
Second type...have a private forum set up.  Once someone is over 300 posts, they may request access to this forum (maybe expand custom titles to cover this also).  Topics are locked so only moderators may post; anytime someone of type 2 is being considered for being banned, a mod sets up a &quot;ban x? yes/no&quot; poll which is locked after 12-24 hours.  If the vote is no, at least 7 days must pass before the person can be considered for banning again.<br>
Just my 2 cp <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
